        <li>Modify or copy the materials</li>
        <li>Use the materials for any commercial purpose or for any public display</li>
        <li>Attempt to reverse engineer any software contained on the website</li>
        <li>Remove any copyright or other proprietary notations from the materials</li>
        <li>Reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from our content without explicit permission</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-[#171717] text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. Content Accuracy</h2>
      <p class="text-[#666] leading-relaxed">
        The materials on AI Tools Hub are provided on an "as is" basis. While we strive for accuracy, we make no warranties, expressed or implied, regarding the completeness, accuracy, reliability, or availability of the information on our website.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[#666] leading-relaxed">
        Product prices, features, and availability are subject to change. We do our best to keep information current, but we recommend verifying details directly with the product's official website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-[#171717] text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p class="text-[#666] leading-relaxed">
        AI Tools Hub contains affiliate links. When you click these links and make a purchase, we may receive a commission. Our editorial opinions are not influenced by affiliate relationships. See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for full details.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-[#171717] text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-[#666] leading-relaxed">
        All content published on AI Tools Hub, including text, graphics, logos, and images, is the property of AI Tools Hub and is protected by international copyright laws. You may not reproduce our content without written permission.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-[#171717] text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-[#666] leading-relaxed">
        In no event shall AI Tools Hub be liable for any damages (including, without limitation, damages for loss of data or profit, or due to business interruption) arising out of the use or inability to use the materials on our website, even if we have been notified orally or in writing of the possibility of such damage.
